      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like everything is just broken. i've tried meds and therapy and nothing works. everywhere i look it just says i should keep trying but i dont feel like my brain is even capable of feeling good anymore. is there a scientific reason why some people just can't get better? like is it actually possible for the brain to just be done?",
